== 事故後續 ==
休班矿工、当地警方及救援人员整理瓦砾以搜寻生还者<ref name="bbc718">{{cite news|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/ukraine-plane-crash/coal-miners-comb-malaysia-airlines-mh17-crash-site-ukraine-n159096|title=Coal Miners Comb Malaysia Airlines MH17 Crash Site in Ukraine|publisher=[[NBC_News|NBC News]]|date=2014-07-18|accessdate=2014-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718105849/http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/ukraine-plane-crash/coal-miners-comb-malaysia-airlines-mh17-crash-site-ukraine-n159096|archive-date=2014-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。出事后，乌克兰关闭东部领空的所有高度的航线<ref name=eurocontrol-20140717>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurocontrol.int/news/mh-17-ukraine|title=MH17 – Ukraine|date=2014-07-17|publisher=Eurocontrol|access-date=2014-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718214251/http://www.eurocontrol.int/news/mh-17-ukraine|archive-date=2014-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年7月18日，当局关闭[[顿涅茨克州|顿涅茨克州]]{{convert|7900|m|ft}}以下空域，7月14日升至{{convert|9800|m|ft}}<ref name=smh-20140718>{{cite news |url=http://www.smh.com.au/business/aviation/mh17-disaster-flights-over-war-zones-because-its-cheaper-20140718-zua0y.html |title=MH17 disaster: Flights over war zones 'because it's cheaper |author=Tom Whitehead, Nick Collins, Martin Evans |newspaper=The Sydney Morning Herald |date=2014-07-18 |accessdate=2014-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140720000307/http://www.smh.com.au/business/aviation/mh17-disaster-flights-over-war-zones-because-its-cheaper-20140718-zua0y.html |archive-date=2014-07-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[欧洲航空安全组织|欧洲航空安全组织]]发表声明，称MH17出事地点位于{{convert|10060|m|ft}}，属限制空域上方<ref name=eurocontrol-20140717/>。

